# ⚠️ SECURITY: Never commit files containing secrets
# If you accidentally committed secrets:
# 1. Immediately rotate ALL affected API keys
# 2. Use git filter-branch or BFG Repo-Cleaner to remove history
# 3. Review security-audit.md for response procedures

